"""Ensure that switching to "FIELD_LIST_COLUMNS_OLD works as
        it should.
        """
with patch.object(saw_14, '_object_fields', new={'dict': 1}):
    out = [(['x'] * len(saw_14.FIELD_LIST_COLUMNS_OLD)) for _ in range(10)]
    with patch.object(saw_14, '_call_simauto', return_value=out):
        result = saw_14.GetFieldList('bus')
self.assertIsInstance(result, pd.DataFrame)
self.assertListEqual(result.columns.tolist(), saw_14.FIELD_LIST_COLUMNS_OLD)
self.assertEqual(result.shape, (10, len(saw_14.FIELD_LIST_COLUMNS_OLD)))
